            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer max-h-0 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out">
          <div class="px-5 sm:px-6 pb-4 sm:pb-5 pt-2">
            <p class="font-sans text-sm sm:text-base text-brand-text leading-relaxed">
              That's exactly why we focus on implementation, not just selling software. We set everything up, train your team, and provide ongoing support. If you can use a smartphone, you can use our systems.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

